You would have to have the 'cast within melee range' requirement because otherwise SOE would never go for it. If you could cast it outside of melee range it would enable us to solo to well (and we know how SOE hates that) - we could just root and nuke with it. <br>
I think maybe adding some aggro reduction to it might be better.<br>
<br>
Other ideas for spells: <br>
- fire and magic based version of the Iceflame of Eci spell.<br>
- something like the rangers 'call of x' line of spells, that adds a fire/cold/magic dd proc to a weapon, only this one would be other targetable. You would have to be very careful with this spell, i.e. make it only work on people fairly close to your level, or scale the damage based on the recipients level. But it would be great for grouping and raids, the tanks would all want it for aggro. Of course then we become buff-ho's. But it would sure make us group-desirable.<br>
- change to rain spells: all the 61+ rain spells should be lure (and it should work), and should not cause root to break. Or maybe make them follow the target.<br>
- Al'Kabor Spells should cause damage to any Developer-GM who is online regardless of what zone they are in. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=glinlor00>Glinlor00</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle><table width=111><tr><td style=filter:glow(color=#6633FF strength=1);font-family:arial;font-weight;bold;font-size:'1pt' nowrap><font size=1 color=#FFFFFF face=Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif>Site Sorcerer</font></td></tr></table><br><table width=111><tr><td style=filter:glow(color=#6633FF strength=1);font-family:arial;font-weight;bold;font-size:'1pt' nowrap><font size=1 color=#FFFFFF face=Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif><a href=mailto:glinlor@graffe.com style=text-decoration: none><font color=#FFFFFF>Contact Glinlor</font></a></font></td></tr></table></span><br>  Posts: 1704<br> <font color=#ffffff>(4/28/03 11:15:00 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=26268.topic&index=31>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Re:Problem</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr><br>
